# Double Tap Exit Fix for Even Realities NBA Pulse

## Problem
Current implementation uses long press for exit functionality, but design requires double tap for exit.

## Solution
Ensure EVENT.DOUBLE_CLICK (eventType: 3) properly triggers exit confirmation and add enhanced debugging.

## Changes

### src/app.js
- Enhanced debug logging to show exact event types and sources
- Added explicit double tap handling confirmation
- Improved event source identification

