### Testing Instructions
1. Build and deploy the app
2. Test double tap gesture on ring/glasses
3. Check console logs for `[DOUBLE-TAP]` and `[RING/GLASSES DEBUG]` messages
4. Verify exit confirmation appears on double tap
5. Confirm single tap still cycles through games

### Expected Behavior
- Single tap → Next game
- Double tap → Exit confirmation  
- Long press → (If supported by hardware) should map to appropriate event

